                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The only Ghost I ever saw</l>
                    <l>Was dressed in Mechlin - so - </l>
                    <l>He had no sandal on his foot - </l>
                    <l>And stepped like flakes of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 snow - </l>
                    <l>His<add type="alternate" extent="Mien,">Gait -</add>
 Mien, was soundless, like<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="the">a -</add>
 the Bird -</l>
                    <l>But rapid - like the Roe - </l>
                    <l>His fashions, quaint, Mosaic - </l>
                    <l>Or haply, Mistletoe - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>His conversation - seldom - </l>
                    <l>His laughter, like the Breeze</l>
                    <l>That dies away in Dimples </l>
                    <l>Among the<add type="alternate" extent="pensive">smiling -</add>
 pensive Trees - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Our interview - was transient -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Of me, himself was shy - </l>
                    <l>And God forbid I look<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 behind -</l>
                    <l>Since that appalling Day!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
